{"word":"ἀναγραμματίζω","slug":"ἀναγραμματίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n6376\" key=\"a)nagrammati/zw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀναγραμματ-ίζω</orth>, <sense id=\"n6376.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">write the letters of a name in direct and then in reverse order,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PMag.Leid.W.\">PMag.Leid.W.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.21</biblScope> </bibl> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram> </gramGrp>), al. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n6376.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">transpose the letters</tr_> of one word so as to form another, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:46:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">46.2</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:488:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">488.12</biblScope> </bibl> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram> </gramGrp>); e. g. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἥρα ἀήρ, ἀρετή ἐρατή, Ἀρσινόη ἴον Ἥρας, Πτολεμαῖος ἀπὸ μέλιτος.</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}